Connection Established
select * from `users` where `id` = 1 limit 1
select exists(select * from `workspace_members` where `user_id` = 1 and `workspace_members`.`deleted_at` is null) as `exists`
select * from `boards` where `boards`.`id` = '1' limit 1

select `users`.*, `board_members`.`board_id` as `pivot_board_id`, `board_members`.`user_id` as `pivot_user_id` from `users` inner join `board_members` on `users`.`id` = `board_members`.`user_id` where `board_members`.`board_id` in (1)
select * from `catalogs` where `catalogs`.`board_id` in (1) and `catalogs`.`deleted_at` is null
select * from `tasks` where `tasks`.`catalog_id` in (1, 2, 11, 20, 29, 38, 47, 56, 65, 74) and `tasks`.`deleted_at` is null order by `position` asc
select `id`, `name` from `catalogs` where `catalogs`.`id` in (1, 2, 11, 20, 29, 38, 47, 56, 65, 74) and `catalogs`.`deleted_at` is null

select `users`.*, `task_members`.`task_id` as `pivot_task_id`, `task_members`.`user_id` as `pivot_user_id` from `users` inner join `task_members` on `users`.`id` = `task_members`.`user_id` where `task_members`.`task_id` in (1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 15, 24, 33, 42, 51, 60, 69, 78)
select * from `check_lists` where `check_lists`.`task_id` in (1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 15, 24, 33, 42, 51, 60, 69, 78)
select * from `check_list_items` where `check_list_items`.`check_list_id` in (1, 2, 3, 4)

select `tags`.*, `task_tags`.`task_id` as `pivot_task_id`, `task_tags`.`tag_id` as `pivot_tag_id` from `tags` inner join `task_tags` on `tags`.`id` = `task_tags`.`tag_id` where `task_tags`.`task_id` in (1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 15, 24, 33, 42, 51, 60, 69, 78)
select * from `follow_members` where `follow_members`.`task_id` in (1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 15, 24, 33, 42, 51, 60, 69, 78)

select `users`.`name`, `users`.`image`, `board_members`.`is_accept_invite`, `board_members`.`authorize`, `users`.`id` as `user_id` from `board_members` inner join `users` on `users`.`id` = `board_members`.`user_id` where `board_members`.`board_id` = 1 and `board_members`.`deleted_at` is null
select * from `colors`
select * from `activity_log` where json_unquote(json_extract(`properties`, '$."board_id"')) = 1 order by `created_at` desc
select * from `users` where `users`.`id` in (1)
select * from `workspace_members` where 0 = 1 and `workspace_id` = 1 and `workspace_members`.`deleted_at` is null
update `board_members` set `is_accept_invite` = 0, `board_members`.`updated_at` = '2024-10-16 14:31:36' where 0 = 1 and `board_id` = 1 and `board_members`.`deleted_at` is null

select `users`.`id`, `users`.`name` from `workspace_members` inner join `users` on `users`.`id` = `workspace_members`.`user_id` left join `board_members` on `workspace_members`.`user_id` = `board_members`.`user_id` and `board_members`.`board_id` = 1 where `board_members`.`user_id` is null and `workspace_members`.`workspace_id` = 1 and `workspace_members`.`authorize` != 'Viewer' and `workspace_members`.`deleted_at` is null

select `workspaces`.*, `workspace_members`.`id` as `workspace_id`, (select count(*) from `workspace_members` where `workspaces`.`id` = `workspace_members`.`workspace_id` and `deleted_at` is null and `workspace_members`.`deleted_at` is null) as `member_count` from `workspaces` inner join `workspace_members` on `workspaces`.`id` = `workspace_members`.`workspace_id` where `workspace_members`.`user_id` = 1 and `workspace_members`.`is_accept_invite` = 0 and not `workspace_members`.`is_active` = 1 and `workspace_members`.`deleted_at` is null group by `workspaces`.`id`, `workspace_members`.`id`

select * from `workspaces` inner join `workspace_members` on `workspaces`.`id` = `workspace_members`.`workspace_id` where `workspace_members`.`user_id` = 1 and `workspace_members`.`is_active` = 1 limit 1
select count(*) as aggregate from `workspace_members` where `workspace_id` = 1 and `workspace_members`.`deleted_at` is null
select `user_id`, `authorize`, `is_accept_invite` from `workspace_members` where `workspace_id` = 1 and `user_id` = 1 and `workspace_members`.`deleted_at` is null limit 1
select * from `workspaces` where `id` = 1 limit 1
select * from `boards` where `boards`.`workspace_id` in (1)

select `is_star` from `board_members` where `board_id` = 1 and `user_id` = 1 and `board_members`.`deleted_at` is null limit 1
